    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小英雄踏上大冒险——《Hela》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/eed85eaa1f6279d4c38dad304967e5ff.poster.avif?t=1770393110\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/eed85eaa1f6279d4c38dad304967e5ff.webm?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/eed85eaa1f6279d4c38dad304967e5ff.mp4?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款迷人的3D合作冒险游戏中，以一只勇敢小老鼠的视角，探索美不胜收的斯堪的纳维亚风光，解开谜题，在这个交织着温馨故事与自然美景的世界中，发挥善良的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善良的女巫生病后，朋友们为拯救她的生命而踏上旅程。扮演一只勇敢的小老鼠，踏上冒险，收集药材，然后调制魔法药水，恢复她的健康。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>共同踏上旅程</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hela》鼓励我们携手克服前方的挑战。你可以选择单人游戏，也可以通过本地多人分屏模式或在线合作模式来与好友合作游戏，从崎岖的山间小径、魔法森林，到静谧湖泊，共同探索郁郁葱葱、生机盎然的风景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/6cb452af60c428ee0aab9818e4299236.poster.avif?t=1770393110\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/6cb452af60c428ee0aab9818e4299236.webm?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/6cb452af60c428ee0aab9818e4299236.mp4?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与编织自己的故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在空中滑翔、收集物品、解开谜题以及面对自然界的种种考验，身临其境地探索这个迷人的世界。随着探索的深入，你将收获更多剧情碎片。行善积德，编织自己的故事，感受自己的影响如同涟漪般在这个世界扩散开来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/231b39f2edf401d055000571cbbbfcfc.poster.avif?t=1770393110\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/231b39f2edf401d055000571cbbbfcfc.webm?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/231b39f2edf401d055000571cbbbfcfc.mp4?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索与发现：</strong>穿越精心制作的广袤地区（灵感源自斯堪的纳维亚），这里遍布魔法森林、静谧湖泊与崎岖山脉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔法背包：</strong>通过可靠的背包与世界交互、收集资源以及解开谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>现实物理：</strong>与表现真实的物品互动，为你的魔法旅程再添沉浸感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生活游乐场：</strong>踏入专为奇妙探索而设的世界，体验互动式物件、蜿蜒小径和各种挑战，满足你的好奇心。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜挑战：</strong>以有趣谜题挑战自己的智慧，这些谜题与剧情无缝结合，在丰富旅程体验、增加挑战的同时为你提供丰厚奖励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小小善举，大大温暖：</strong>善良本身就是最好的回报。在细微的善举中寻找意义，感受其中的静谧温暖。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>共同畅玩：</strong>你可以单独体验旅程，也可以通过分屏或在线模式与好友共同游戏。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/512b4001bd0f72b605e726503e88197d.poster.avif?t=1770393110\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/512b4001bd0f72b605e726503e88197d.webm?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161310/extras/512b4001bd0f72b605e726503e88197d.mp4?t=1770393110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
